# This directory holds pre-trained model files.
# All files below are included in this repository.
#
# === Religion models (religion.ipynb / run_py38.py) ===
#
# Binary classification (2class):
#   vectorizer_2class_svm_concat_False.sav   — TF-IDF vectorizer (single name)
#   model_2class_svm_concat_False.sav        — SVM classifier (single name)
#   vectorizer_2class_svm_concat_True.sav    — TF-IDF vectorizer (concatenated names)
#   model_2class_svm_concat_True.sav         — SVM classifier (concatenated names)
#
# Multiclass classification:
#   vectorizer_multiclass_svm_concat_False.sav
#   model_multiclass_svm_concat_False.sav
#   vectorizer_multiclass_svm_concat_True.sav
#   model_multiclass_svm_concat_True.sav
#   non_neural_label_encoding_multiclass.pkl — label encoder for multiclass mode
#
# Tokenizers (religion, character-level):
#   tokenizer_binary_False.pkl
#   tokenizer_binary_True.pkl
#   tokenizer_multiclass_False.pkl
#   tokenizer_multiclass_True.pkl
#
# === Race/ethnicity models (race.ipynb) ===
#
#   cnn_USA_text.h5          — CNN text-only model
#   cnn_USA_meta.h5          — CNN with GIS/demographic priors
#   nc_voter_encoding.pkl    — Label encoder
#   nc_voter_tokenizer.pkl   — Character-level tokenizer
